 project due to the tight deadline, but the time spent to organize all requirements was crucial to the accuracy of the project. It was possible to see the value in following the flow of organization of prototypes, creating a stlye guide, componentizing colors, fonts and elements, and then saving time during the project. Making efficient prototypes with interactive flows, so the validations with PO and developers were quick and effective, providing a success in the final delivery, a satisfied customer and a design project delivered on time."}]';

